spirit:component.spirit:name: v6_gtxwizard_v1_12
spirit:component.spirit:description: Use the Virtex-6 FPGA GTX Transceiver Wizard to configure one or more Virtex-6 FPGA GTX transceivers. Start from scratch, or use an industry standard template. The Wizard generates a custom wrapper for the tranceivers you've selected. In addition, it produces an example design, testbench, and scripts to observe the transceivers operating under simulation and in hardware.
